{
  "texts": [
    "We choose seven medical LLMs with different numbers of parameters and different types of fine-tuning data.",
    "In detail, as shown in Table 3, ChatGLM-Med (Wang et al., 2023b) and DoctorGLM (Xiong et al., 2023) are fine-tuned on the ChatGLM-6B (Tsinghua KEG, 2023; Du et al., 2022; Zeng et al., 2022) using QA pairs and dialogues, respectively.",
    "Huatuo (Zhang et al., 2023a), ChatDoctor (Li et al., 2023b), Baize-Healthcare (Xu et al., 2023), and MedAlpaca-7B/13B (Han et al., 2023) are built upon the LLaMA-series models.",
    "During finetuning, both Huatuo and MedAlpaca employ the QA pairs collected from the medical knowledge graphs and medical texts, respectively.",
    "ChatDoctor and Baize-Healthcare are fine-tuned on medical dialogues generated by commercial LLMs (e.g., ChatGPT)."
  ]
}